>>PARTI: Yeah, I've
been to his house.

00:01:02.950 --> 00:01:07.090 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Yes, and he's a lovely
gentleman, and because you're

00:01:07.090 --> 00:01:09.160 align:middle line:10%
