00:44:41.127 --> 00:44:43.710 align:middle line:84%
So my wife said, [NON-ENGLISH]
do you want to give it a chance

00:44:43.710 --> 00:44:46.480 align:middle line:90%
and finish 30 years of marriage?

00:44:46.480 --> 00:44:47.310 align:middle line:90%
I said, why not?

00:44:47.310 --> 00:44:50.000 align:middle line:84%
I've lived with you for so
long, had three kids with you,

00:44:50.000 --> 00:44:51.310 align:middle line:90%
let's give it a shot.

00:44:51.310 --> 00:44:56.640 align:middle line:84%
And from there, I
was now Raj 3.0.

00:44:56.640 --> 00:44:59.430 align:middle line:84%
I had started applying
the lessons I had learned

00:44:59.430 --> 00:45:01.290 align:middle line:90%
from near-death experience.

00:45:01.290 --> 00:45:04.680 align:middle line:84%
The biggest lesson was
the power of forgiveness.

00:45:04.680 --> 00:45:08.770 align:middle line:84%
And I became a kinder, and I
started practicing forgiveness,

00:45:08.770 --> 00:45:14.330 align:middle line:84%
that she realized that
she can really love me.

00:45:14.330 --> 00:45:15.700 align:middle line:90%
And it was like a fairy tale.

00:45:15.700 --> 00:45:19.340 align:middle line:84%
Then six weeks later,
on 12th February,

00:45:19.340 --> 00:45:21.740 align:middle line:90%
we burned the divorce papers.

00:45:21.740 --> 00:45:23.470 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You burned
the divorce papers?

00:45:23.470 --> 00:45:24.270 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: Like a--

00:45:24.270 --> 00:45:25.880 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah,
a little bonfire.

00:45:25.880 --> 00:45:27.700 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: A bonfire.

00:45:27.700 --> 00:45:29.315 align:middle line:84%
In India, we do
bonfires with mantras,

00:45:29.315 --> 00:45:32.787 align:middle line:84%
so we were let it go,
like, past is past.

00:45:32.787 --> 00:45:34.370 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So what
happened between you

00:45:34.370 --> 00:45:36.320 align:middle line:84%
that allowed you to
feel each other again,

00:45:36.320 --> 00:45:38.000 align:middle line:90%
besides that one decision?

00:45:38.000 --> 00:45:40.190 align:middle line:90%
After that decision?

00:45:40.190 --> 00:45:41.547 align:middle line:90%
What opened up again?

00:45:41.547 --> 00:45:43.130 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: You know
what opened up again

00:45:43.130 --> 00:45:48.380 align:middle line:84%
was our communication and
power of forgiveness and love.

00:45:48.380 --> 00:45:52.370 align:middle line:84%
Because when I took my wife
out for dinner the evening

00:45:52.370 --> 00:45:56.690 align:middle line:84%
we were reconciling, I said
what do you want from me?

00:45:56.690 --> 00:45:59.270 align:middle line:90%
And she said three words.

00:45:59.270 --> 00:46:01.850 align:middle line:90%
Respect, care, and love.

00:46:01.850 --> 00:46:04.290 align:middle line:84%
And the order she said it
was very important, too.

00:46:04.290 --> 00:46:05.090 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:46:05.090 --> 00:46:06.506 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: She wants
to be respected

00:46:06.506 --> 00:46:08.520 align:middle line:84%
as an equal,
different but equal,

00:46:08.520 --> 00:46:12.420 align:middle line:84%
she wants to be cherished and
cared for, and then loved also.

00:46:12.420 --> 00:46:13.220 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:46:13.220 --> 00:46:15.110 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: And
previously I loved her,

00:46:15.110 --> 00:46:17.810 align:middle line:84%
but coming from an
Indian background,

00:46:17.810 --> 00:46:20.260 align:middle line:84%
coming from my
father's generations,

00:46:20.260 --> 00:46:24.920 align:middle line:84%
and that was what I call
a vertical relationship.

00:46:24.920 --> 00:46:26.890 align:middle line:84%
Husband at top, then
the wife, and then kids.

00:46:26.890 --> 00:46:27.690 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:46:27.690 --> 00:46:30.200 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: So now it was a
horizontal relationship,

00:46:30.200 --> 00:46:32.950 align:middle line:84%
me and you are
equal but different.

00:46:32.950 --> 00:46:33.750 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:46:33.750 --> 00:46:35.750 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: And I started
cherishing her,

00:46:35.750 --> 00:46:40.850 align:middle line:84%
sending her flowers for no
reason, just to say I love you,

00:46:40.850 --> 00:46:43.400 align:middle line:90%
and now I'm so happy.

00:46:43.400 --> 00:46:45.790 align:middle line:84%
In last one and a
half, two years,

00:46:45.790 --> 00:46:48.104 align:middle line:84%
it has been the best time
in 30 years of our marriage.

00:46:48.104 --> 00:46:49.520 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You said
off-camera when

00:46:49.520 --> 00:46:52.210 align:middle line:84%
we were talking that it's
like you're teenagers again.

00:46:52.210 --> 00:46:54.410 align:middle line:90%
You're in love anew.

00:46:54.410 --> 00:46:57.440 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: You know, if
you look at my text,

00:46:57.440 --> 00:47:01.485 align:middle line:84%
when we put the code
for Wi-Fi, there

00:47:01.485 --> 00:47:04.040 align:middle line:84%
were 10 texts which came up,
and they were all from my wife.

00:47:04.040 --> 00:47:06.550 align:middle line:84%
I love you, you'll
do good, miss you,

00:47:06.550 --> 00:47:10.550 align:middle line:84%
with all hearts and
everything, emojis of hearts.

00:47:10.550 --> 00:47:11.510 align:middle line:90%
That's like teenagers.

00:47:11.510 --> 00:47:14.690 align:middle line:84%
We have to text each other
almost every two hours.

00:47:14.690 --> 00:47:17.630 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But you had to really
tear yourself down to the bones

00:47:17.630 --> 00:47:20.200 align:middle line:84%
of what you were as
a being, as a soul--

00:47:20.200 --> 00:47:21.000 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: Exactly.

00:47:21.000 --> 00:47:22.670 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: --to get there.

00:47:22.670 --> 00:47:24.750 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: I had to
remake myself again.

00:47:24.750 --> 00:47:26.570 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So let's
talk about now.

00:47:26.570 --> 00:47:29.390 align:middle line:84%
You have this book
out, and how you're

00:47:29.390 --> 00:47:31.910 align:middle line:84%
putting yourself into the
world and working with people.

00:47:31.910 --> 00:47:35.090 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: Now what happened,
was because of my heartbreak

00:47:35.090 --> 00:47:37.940 align:middle line:84%
and healing people's
heart, and my heart

00:47:37.940 --> 00:47:41.930 align:middle line:84%
was healed, using the lessons
from my physical near-death

00:47:41.930 --> 00:47:45.680 align:middle line:84%
experience, I'm helping
people, especially

00:47:45.680 --> 00:47:49.790 align:middle line:84%
women who are coming to me
more now, with heartbreaks.

00:47:49.790 --> 00:47:52.380 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, heart
disease is on the rise.

00:47:52.380 --> 00:47:55.400 align:middle line:84%
Huge, dramatic increase
in heart disease in women.

00:47:55.400 --> 00:47:56.810 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: Because of stress.

00:47:56.810 --> 00:47:58.940 align:middle line:84%
People used to think
that heart disease is

00:47:58.940 --> 00:48:01.770 align:middle line:90%
a disease of the male.

00:48:01.770 --> 00:48:03.670 align:middle line:90%
A plus personality.

00:48:03.670 --> 00:48:08.190 align:middle line:84%
But it's equally
prominent among women.

00:48:08.190 --> 00:48:10.040 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:48:10.040 --> 00:48:10.890 align:middle line:90%
I've looked at that.

00:48:10.890 --> 00:48:14.900 align:middle line:84%
And it seems to me part of it
is that we still, as beings,

00:48:14.900 --> 00:48:19.190 align:middle line:84%
as human beings and souls, have
the same needs, like she said,

00:48:19.190 --> 00:48:22.610 align:middle line:84%
to have the love, to be
cherished, to have respect

00:48:22.610 --> 00:48:23.660 align:middle line:90%
and so forth.

00:48:23.660 --> 00:48:26.690 align:middle line:84%
Yet what happened
over the last 40 years

00:48:26.690 --> 00:48:30.020 align:middle line:84%
is that the women became
really almost the dominant part

00:48:30.020 --> 00:48:31.431 align:middle line:90%
of the workforce.

00:48:31.431 --> 00:48:33.680 align:middle line:84%
And yet you still have the
children you have to raise.

00:48:33.680 --> 00:48:35.600 align:middle line:84%
You still have to do
what else has to be done,

00:48:35.600 --> 00:48:37.975 align:middle line:84%
depending on the amount of
money you make, cook and clean

00:48:37.975 --> 00:48:41.830 align:middle line:84%
and so forth, and the stress
is absolutely overwhelming.

00:48:41.830 --> 00:48:43.370 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: Overwhelming.

00:48:43.370 --> 00:48:45.920 align:middle line:90%
Too much is expected of women.

00:48:45.920 --> 00:48:47.960 align:middle line:84%
Giving an example,
I'm being a partner

00:48:47.960 --> 00:48:49.850 align:middle line:90%
with her and everything.

00:48:49.850 --> 00:48:52.460 align:middle line:84%
Previously I would
sit while she was

00:48:52.460 --> 00:48:54.590 align:middle line:90%
cooking after coming home work.

00:48:54.590 --> 00:48:56.750 align:middle line:84%
But now, I don't
know how to cook,

00:48:56.750 --> 00:48:58.770 align:middle line:84%
but I'm cutting
her vegetables, I'm

00:48:58.770 --> 00:49:00.560 align:middle line:84%
getting her the
things she needs,

00:49:00.560 --> 00:49:03.020 align:middle line:84%
I'm peeling the
vegetables, chopping

00:49:03.020 --> 00:49:04.700 align:middle line:90%
the onions, whatever I can.

00:49:04.700 --> 00:49:07.586 align:middle line:84%
So I'm with her in the
kitchen, and she loves it.

00:49:07.586 --> 00:49:08.960 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yes,
that makes cooking

00:49:08.960 --> 00:49:10.964 align:middle line:90%
a joy instead of a drudgery.

00:49:10.964 --> 00:49:12.380 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: Yeah,
it's a partnership.

00:49:12.380 --> 00:49:12.860 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:49:12.860 --> 00:49:15.165 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: So now what we
have is true partnership

00:49:15.165 --> 00:49:16.910 align:middle line:90%
and friendship.

00:49:16.910 --> 00:49:18.737 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And she's a
dentist, as I recall?

00:49:18.737 --> 00:49:19.820 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: She is a dentist.

00:49:19.820 --> 00:49:21.680 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: She's so she's
still doing her day job.

00:49:21.680 --> 00:49:22.480 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: Yeah.

00:49:22.480 --> 00:49:25.340 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But your day job
now, do you have an office

00:49:25.340 --> 00:49:26.750 align:middle line:90%
or a clinic or how does--

00:49:26.750 --> 00:49:28.760 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: I'm moving to
Santa Cruz right now,

00:49:28.760 --> 00:49:30.770 align:middle line:84%
so I'm going to take
up an office there,

00:49:30.770 --> 00:49:33.640 align:middle line:84%
but right now I work primarily
through Skype and on phone.

00:49:33.640 --> 00:49:34.440 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:49:34.440 --> 00:49:36.920 align:middle line:84%
And so when people
find you, what

00:49:36.920 --> 00:49:39.260 align:middle line:84%
is the process you take
them through in your work,

00:49:39.260 --> 00:49:42.260 align:middle line:84%
and what do they most
profoundly respond to?

00:49:42.260 --> 00:49:44.930 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: You know,
as most of my clients

00:49:44.930 --> 00:49:47.510 align:middle line:84%
are women, for some
reason, and they're

00:49:47.510 --> 00:49:51.200 align:middle line:84%
been traumatized by different
males in their life,

00:49:51.200 --> 00:49:54.380 align:middle line:84%
and I help them
empower themselves.

00:49:54.380 --> 00:49:58.380 align:middle line:84%
Like archetypal work, or
deal with childhood traumas,

00:49:58.380 --> 00:50:00.690 align:middle line:90%
because there's so much abuse.

00:50:00.690 --> 00:50:04.010 align:middle line:84%
And that has-- the
universe is opening me.

00:50:04.010 --> 00:50:06.500 align:middle line:84%
I didn't start with
working with women,

00:50:06.500 --> 00:50:10.562 align:middle line:84%
but that's what is getting
attracted towards me.

00:50:10.562 --> 00:50:16.042 align:middle line:84%
To help women, I as a male
hold safe space for them.

00:50:16.042 --> 00:50:18.500 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Which is interesting,
because that isn't what you

00:50:18.500 --> 00:50:19.812 align:middle line:90%
expected was going to happen.

00:50:19.812 --> 00:50:21.770 align:middle line:84%
You thought you would be
able to help, perhaps,

00:50:21.770 --> 00:50:24.390 align:middle line:84%
even some of your colleagues
after they fell down and became

00:50:24.390 --> 00:50:25.190 align:middle line:90%
ill.

00:50:25.190 --> 00:50:25.520 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: Yeah.

00:50:25.520 --> 00:50:26.960 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But they're not
the ones coming to you.

00:50:26.960 --> 00:50:29.040 align:middle line:84%
The men aren't coming
in the same way.

00:50:29.040 --> 00:50:31.280 align:middle line:84%
They're not looking
for healing and help

00:50:31.280 --> 00:50:32.790 align:middle line:90%
in the same way women are now.

00:50:32.790 --> 00:50:33.590 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: Yeah.

00:50:33.590 --> 00:50:35.990 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: What are you seeing
about that and how that's

00:50:35.990 --> 00:50:39.170 align:middle line:84%
lining up, and then looking
down at your children's

00:50:39.170 --> 00:50:41.570 align:middle line:90%
generation, the differences?

00:50:41.570 --> 00:50:43.900 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: Yeah, like my
children, my daughter

00:50:43.900 --> 00:50:46.260 align:middle line:90%
she is a very strong woman.

00:50:46.260 --> 00:50:49.280 align:middle line:84%
I actually named her
after a goddess in India,

00:50:49.280 --> 00:50:52.990 align:middle line:84%
and she turned out to be,
even I can't handle her.

00:50:52.990 --> 00:50:55.920 align:middle line:84%
She's so powerful and
strong, but she's very kind.

00:50:55.920 --> 00:50:56.720 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:50:56.720 --> 00:50:59.570 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: And that's what
I want my clients to be,

00:50:59.570 --> 00:51:02.420 align:middle line:90%
equal respectful for male--

00:51:02.420 --> 00:51:04.700 align:middle line:90%
masculine, and noblemen.

00:51:04.700 --> 00:51:07.820 align:middle line:84%
Men should be noblemen,
women should be like goddess,

00:51:07.820 --> 00:51:10.650 align:middle line:84%
and they can be in partnership
and everybody will be happy.

00:51:10.650 --> 00:51:11.450 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:51:11.450 --> 00:51:15.170 align:middle line:84%
So now in your son's
generation, are

00:51:15.170 --> 00:51:17.720 align:middle line:84%
you noticing in your
own life and circle,

00:51:17.720 --> 00:51:20.225 align:middle line:84%
and also among your
clients, that--

00:51:20.225 --> 00:51:22.430 align:middle line:84%
because there is a
generational divide

00:51:22.430 --> 00:51:24.200 align:middle line:84%
in this, of the
women taking it all

00:51:24.200 --> 00:51:26.450 align:middle line:90%
on with no help from the men.

00:51:26.450 --> 00:51:28.550 align:middle line:84%
Are you finding
that the younger men

00:51:28.550 --> 00:51:32.400 align:middle line:84%
are more oriented toward
true partnership now?

00:51:32.400 --> 00:51:35.630 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: Yeah, my
daughter has a boyfriend,

00:51:35.630 --> 00:51:38.330 align:middle line:84%
and I write in my book,
actually, my daughter's

00:51:38.330 --> 00:51:39.470 align:middle line:90%
boyfriend is a Muslim.

00:51:39.470 --> 00:51:41.840 align:middle line:84%
I would have never
accepted that.

00:51:41.840 --> 00:51:43.730 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Oh, yeah,
that's a big one.

00:51:43.730 --> 00:51:45.530 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: Before my
near-death experience.

00:51:45.530 --> 00:51:46.330 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:51:46.330 --> 00:51:48.710 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: But now I accept that.

00:51:48.710 --> 00:51:49.790 align:middle line:90%
Everybody's equal.

00:51:49.790 --> 00:51:52.190 align:middle line:90%
Everybody has the same rights.

00:51:52.190 --> 00:51:55.000 align:middle line:84%
And I wouldn't have accepted
that before, to be honest,

00:51:55.000 --> 00:51:58.480 align:middle line:84%
but coming from that
partnership story I just told.

00:51:58.480 --> 00:52:00.700 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:52:00.700 --> 00:52:04.670 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: But my daughter expects
her boyfriend to be a partner,

00:52:04.670 --> 00:52:08.090 align:middle line:84%
and he is a partner, helping
my daughter all the time.

00:52:08.090 --> 00:52:13.190 align:middle line:84%
And a partnership, like somebody
is sick, you do the thing.

00:52:13.190 --> 00:52:16.100 align:middle line:84%
I cannot cook, so when
my wife is very tired,

00:52:16.100 --> 00:52:17.850 align:middle line:84%
I go and bring the
food from outside.

00:52:17.850 --> 00:52:20.270 align:middle line:90%
She feels cared for.

00:52:20.270 --> 00:52:21.820 align:middle line:90%
She feels loved.

00:52:21.820 --> 00:52:25.710 align:middle line:90%
And even love is not a noun.

00:52:25.710 --> 00:52:26.580 align:middle line:90%
It's a verb.

00:52:26.580 --> 00:52:28.450 align:middle line:90%
It is doing.

00:52:28.450 --> 00:52:30.270 align:middle line:90%
It is a state of doing.

00:52:30.270 --> 00:52:31.140 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:52:31.140 --> 00:52:35.055 align:middle line:84%
And so now what
do you recommend?

00:52:35.055 --> 00:52:38.010 align:middle line:84%
Do you also have people
work with meditation

00:52:38.010 --> 00:52:40.280 align:middle line:84%
in almost all
cases in your life?

00:52:40.280 --> 00:52:41.970 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: Yeah, all
of my clients I

00:52:41.970 --> 00:52:45.030 align:middle line:84%
help them start a
meditation practice,

00:52:45.030 --> 00:52:47.040 align:middle line:84%
because meditation
is when you connect

00:52:47.040 --> 00:52:53.120 align:middle line:84%
to the stillness, the awareness
within you which is unchanging.

00:52:53.120 --> 00:52:55.020 align:middle line:90%
The higher self.

00:52:55.020 --> 00:52:57.790 align:middle line:84%
If you believe in God or
soul, then it is your soul,

00:52:57.790 --> 00:53:00.590 align:middle line:84%
and you are part of
the spark of God.

00:53:00.590 --> 00:53:03.510 align:middle line:84%
Like in Bible they say
the kingdom of heaven

00:53:03.510 --> 00:53:04.420 align:middle line:90%
is within you.

00:53:04.420 --> 00:53:05.220 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:53:05.220 --> 00:53:06.540 align:middle line:90%
>>PARTI: So it is within you.

00:53:06.540 --> 00:53:09.500 align:middle line:84%
But if you don't believe
in your higher self or God,

00:53:09.500 --> 00:53:11.410 align:middle line:84%
at least you believe
in your own self.

00:53:11.410 --> 00:53:12.210 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:53:12.210 --> 00:53:15.030 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: And that's my
thing is empowerment.

00:53:15.030 --> 00:53:18.150 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Now when you started
opening this up in yourself,

00:53:18.150 --> 00:53:21.360 align:middle line:84%
and direct communication with
your soul and beings beyond,

00:53:21.360 --> 00:53:25.170 align:middle line:84%
did you ever then come back
in contact with your father?

00:53:25.170 --> 00:53:30.030 align:middle line:84%
>>PARTI: I have met my
father in dreams and visions,

00:53:30.030 --> 00:53:32.280 align:middle line:90%
and he has been very helpful.

00:53:32.280 --> 00:53:36.350 align:middle line:84%
Like if I've-- even
in worldly things,

00:53:36.350 --> 00:53:38.640 align:middle line:84%
like I would like
to have a sign,

00:53:38.640 --> 00:53:42.450 align:middle line:84%
like if I'm starting a spiritual
practice or if I'm going to buy

00:53:42.450 --> 00:53:46.530 align:middle line:84%
a different house,
show me a sign.

